text.tspan: Ocean Beach will be raging tomorrow
Get ready to hop on your board, the latest
forecasts are in. Expect 23 knots by 3pm.
Kelly’s Cove should be kiteable later today
There should be wind gusts upwards of 20 knots
with a steady 17 knots from 1pm to 4pm.
Look out for Stinson Beach this weekend
Exciting forecast for the next two days up North,
25 knots with gusts at 28. Get flying!
